  <brief_title>Impact of a Decision Aid on Patient Decision Making in Emergency Department Chest Pain Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Impact of a Decision Aid on Patient Participation in Decision Making and Resource Use in Low Risk Chest Pain Patients: A Randomized Trial</official_title>
